colnames(serotype)= c("H Antigen", "O Antigen")
kable(serotype, results='asis', align = "c")
\`\`\`

<br>

[Back to index](#index)

EOF
	else
cat <<EOF >> $OUTWD/report_files/tormes_report.Rmd

WARNING: serotyping for *Escherichia* was not performed.

